28:14.601 --> 28:17.269
meet a friend next month,
but I'm kinda broke.

28:17.645 --> 28:19.187
You should ask Larry for the cash.

28:19.355 --> 28:21.607
Ooh no, that's not my style.

28:24.277 --> 28:25.736
Have you ever been to Europe.

28:26.571 --> 28:28.405
I've been to Florida once.

28:28.615 --> 28:31.241
And that time your parents took
me to Mexico.

28:31.451 --> 28:33.452
- That's about it.
- That's right, that's right.

28:34.078 --> 28:36.163
- I don't travel much.
- You should go, man.

28:37.582 --> 28:38.916
I'd like to someday.

28:39.083 --> 28:41.418
I mean, just for the art.
-Yeah.

28:45.340 --> 28:46.298
Hmm.

28:46.841 --> 28:48.175
Go ahead, take it.

28:49.177 --> 28:50.677
Nah, it's cool.

28:51.763 --> 28:54.264
