- Takes a little practice.

29:03.483 --> 29:05.567
And he drives right through
the stop sign.

29:05.735 --> 29:09.237
And out into some field.
He totally passed out.

29:09.322 --> 29:10.614
He must've been wasted, man.

29:10.782 --> 29:12.991
He was totally hammered.
He's a fucking idiot.

29:15.578 --> 29:17.996
But he's my brother.
And I love him.

29:18.206 --> 29:19.790
And my best friend.

29:19.958 --> 29:21.208
- Cheers!
- Cheers!

29:23.586 --> 29:25.045
I'm gonna get another... you?

29:25.171 --> 29:26.463
- Mhmm, Ok.
- Alright.

29:45.066 --> 29:46.149
Here you go...

29:46.526 --> 29:47.609
Thanks, brother.

29:47.777 --> 29:49.778
- Wow.
- Woah... what are you doing?

29:49.946 --> 29:53.031
Easy dude, it's ok.
I wanna look at it.

29:53.199 --> 29:54.908
No one ever looks at that.

30:08.131 --> 30:09.506
Wow, is that Cody?

30:11.801 --> 30:12.676
Yeah.

30:15.930 --> 30:17.305
A sad Cody.

30:20.601 --> 30:21.727
You could tell?

30:21.769 --> 30:23.854
Yeah. And how you darkened it
around his head.

30:24.355 --> 30:25.647
This is incredible.

30:27.483 --> 30:29.526
And there's no toys in his room.

30:31.529 --> 30:32.404
Wow.

30:36.743 --> 30:37.826
It's awesome.

30:41.873 --> 30:46.585
Yeah, he'd just gotten scolded.
He was trying to understand why...

30:48.337 --> 30:50.047
So he came into my room.

30:53.259 --> 30:55.719
He hasn't left yet.
It's the only place he could sleep.

30:58.014 --> 30:59.097
Ok, enough.

31:13.071 --> 31:15.113
Ow, ho ho, ow.

31:15.281 --> 31:16.031
Ow!

31:16.199 --> 31:17.532
Adam's apple.

31:20.995 --> 31:24.081
- I'm trashed.
- The cops are definitely coming.

32:15.800 --> 32:17.175
Shit!

32:41.951 --> 32:42.951
What? You'll make it.

32:42.952 --> 32:44.286
Cody, let's go.

32:45.621 --> 32:46.580
Where were you?

32:46.622 --> 32:47.789
- Surfing.
- All night?

32:47.957 --> 32:49.249
Yeah, what the fuck?

32:50.168 --> 32:51.209
I'm just asking.

32:51.377 --> 32:52.627
- Want a ride or not?
- Go.

32:52.712 --> 32:53.837
Cody, let's go!

32:57.592 --> 32:59.509
I think I should reapply
to CalArts...

32:59.510 --> 33:00.594
What's CalArts?

33:00.636 --> 33:02.012
It's a school, buddy.

33:02.180 --> 33:04.973
- I get to go to school next year.
- Yep.

33:05.266 --> 33:06.766
They already turned you down.

33:07.768 --> 33:09.227
What made you think of that?

33:09.228 --> 33:10.604
It's just a thought.

33:12.565 --> 33:13.899
Well don't get your hopes up.

33:15.568 --> 33:19.112
I mean we're having a hard time, Zach.
I don't need you getting all down.

33:19.447 --> 33:20.447
Yeah...

33:21.782 --> 33:24.951
Alan paints houses. Maybe I can see if
he can hook you up with a job.

33:29.081 --> 33:29.915
Ooh.

33:31.042 --> 33:32.292
You're heavy.

33:35.922 --> 33:36.796
Come on.

33:39.050 --> 33:41.301
- I'll be right in.
- Alright, hurry up.

33:41.469 --> 33:42.677
Hey, monkey.

33:43.554 --> 33:44.721
Hey.

33:47.767 --> 33:49.142
I'm late.

35:28.617 --> 35:30.118
Hey.

35:30.119 --> 35:31.619
Oh hey.

35:31.787 --> 35:33.663
I hear you've been hanging
out with Shaun.

35:34.874 --> 35:36.374
Surfing.

35:36.417 --> 35:37.917
Well you know about him, right?

35:38.044 --> 35:39.252
What about him?

35:40.171 --> 35:41.504
He's gay.

35:41.672 --> 35:44.466
He's an old friend, Jeanne. We've been
surfing together since I was 8.

35:44.550 --> 35:45.717
Yeah, well is that all?

35:45.801 --> 35:48.094
Yeah, what are you saying?

35:48.346 --> 35:49.846
- Nothing.
- Good.

35:51.390 --> 35:53.725
Zach, I just don't think that he's

35:53.893 --> 35:56.895
the best guy to be hanging out with
all day half-naked...

35:57.104 --> 36:00.106
if you know what I mean.
And I don't want Cody around that.

36:00.274 --> 36:01.983
What? Why?

36:04.403 --> 36:05.945
I'm late. Get out.

36:06.030 --> 36:07.155
Fine.

36:20.586 --> 36:22.420
Zach, you're not a fag, right?

36:22.797 --> 36:23.713
Jeanne...

36:23.881 --> 36:26.091
Wait, you never tell me anything.
How am I supposed to know?

36:26.092 --> 36:27.425
What do you think?

36:28.344 --> 36:30.136
I think I don't wanna deal with that.

36:52.868 --> 36:54.369
Hi dude.

36:54.829 --> 36:56.663
- I tried calling you.
- Yeah.

36:58.916 --> 37:01.584
- Listen, I just wanted to...
- Yeah, I've been really busy, man.

37:02.586 --> 37:05.422
- Yeah, that's cool.
- Yeah, I know.

37:06.590 --> 37:08.800
- Listen, man...
- Just drop it, dude.

37:11.470 --> 37:12.637
Ok.

37:19.478 --> 37:20.728
Hey, Shaun.

37:21.188 --> 37:23.231
Hey. What's up?

37:23.566 --> 37:24.899
I need help!

37:24.942 --> 37:26.401
Shaun, this is Cody.

37:27.069 --> 37:28.736
Hi Cody, how are you, man?
I'm Shaun.

37:28.779 --> 37:29.821
I need help.

37:29.822 --> 37:31.156
You need help?

37:32.491 --> 37:34.367
Uhh, alright...

37:35.619 --> 37:37.328
But, dude you've got it all wrong.

37:37.830 --> 37:41.374
See, you've gotta fortify the corners
of the moat first.

37:41.584 --> 37:43.126
"Fourty-fi"?

37:43.294 --> 37:45.211
Codes, let's go.

37:45.421 --> 37:48.339
I'm not done; I have to "fourty-fi"!

37:49.300 --> 37:51.342
Shaun, do you mind looking after
Cody for a second?

37:51.802 --> 37:52.969
We're cool.

37:53.554 --> 37:54.721
Let's go for a walk.

37:55.014 --> 37:56.514
No, I don't think I should leave Cody.

37:56.640 --> 37:57.849
Come on, Shaun can watch him.

37:59.310 --> 38:01.519
You guys go, it's fine.

38:04.565 --> 38:05.815
Alright.

38:06.192 --> 38:07.358
There we go.

38:07.526 --> 38:10.695
This is gonna be a sweet walking
bridge. Oh look at that!

38:14.617 --> 38:16.409
Shaun's great with Cody.

38:20.581 --> 38:22.540
Listen, I'm sorry about the other day.

38:26.045 --> 38:27.462
It was stupid.

38:28.506 --> 38:30.298
Just make up your mind, Zach.

38:31.133 --> 38:34.761
If you don't want to be together then
just don't pull that shit on me.

38:37.973 --> 38:39.098
Ok.

38:41.602 --> 38:44.187
If it's what you want then
I'm gonna move on.

38:46.565 --> 38:47.649
Alright.

38:48.984 --> 38:50.777
You know what that means, right?

38:51.570 --> 38:53.655
Yeah, Tori. I know what that means.

38:54.865 --> 38:55.990
Just go, ok?

39:00.079 --> 39:01.621
Come on, Cody.
Time to go.

39:01.789 --> 39:03.081
Five more minutes.

39:03.249 --> 39:04.040
Shaun rocks.

39:04.083 --> 39:05.625
No, Cody. Let's go.

39:05.876 --> 39:07.085
Shaun rocks!

39:08.003 --> 39:09.796
Can I jump on the sand castle?

39:10.005 --> 39:11.214
No, we gotta go. Come on.

39:11.382 --> 39:14.509
Hey, the tide's gonna get it anyway.
You might as well let him have at it.

39:15.761 --> 39:17.011
Go ahead.

39:17.179 --> 39:19.389
- Woo!
- Weehaa!

39:23.519 --> 39:25.103
Alright man, great job!

39:26.397 --> 39:27.814
Come on, little man.

39:28.315 --> 39:29.357
Sayonara.

39:30.150 --> 39:33.152
Hey, I just wanted to talk
to you about the other night.

39:35.197 --> 39:36.281
What?

39:36.448 --> 39:39.909
I think you're really talented. And I
don't think you should throw it away.

39:40.077 --> 39:41.452
I think you should do something
with it.

39:41.537 --> 39:42.620
Is that it?

39:44.873 --> 39:45.873
Yeah.

39:46.959 --> 39:48.126
I'm late.

39:59.096 --> 39:59.887
Tori, I'll call...

42:16.984 --> 42:18.109
Good morning.

42:20.028 --> 42:21.237
What time is it?

42:24.533 --> 42:26.159
Why? You got somewhere to go?

42:26.744 --> 42:30.204
Yeah. Yeah I gotta go.

42:31.582 --> 42:33.082
Wait.

42:34.793 --> 42:36.711
Listen, I gotta go.

43:20.589 --> 43:22.840
- Hey, Jeannie.
- Hey.

43:26.261 --> 43:27.512
Where's Cody?

43:27.679 --> 43:29.222
Like you care.

43:29.389 --> 43:30.848
What are you talking about?

43:31.058 --> 43:33.434
Where were you last night?
I called you like 3 times.

43:33.685 --> 43:34.852
Did you need something?

43:35.020 --> 43:37.688
Yeah. I need to know you're there.

43:37.856 --> 43:39.565
I'm always there. For Cody.

43:39.817 --> 43:41.192
You weren't last night.

43:44.488 --> 43:45.863
What do you need, Jeannie?

43:48.283 --> 43:50.785
Actually, Alan is going up
to Portland this weekend.

43:50.953 --> 43:53.871
And um, he's gonna make a bid on a
job. He said he'd take me.

43:54.748 --> 43:56.791
It would do me so much good
to get out of here.

43:57.417 --> 43:59.043
- Alan?
- Yeah.

44:00.254 --> 44:02.922
- Alan?
- Uh huh.

44:04.299 --> 44:06.551
Can you watch Cody this weekend?
Please...

44:07.135 --> 44:09.762
You know, I was hoping to have
the weekend to myself.

44:09.805 --> 44:11.055
Why?

44:11.640 --> 44:13.349
Who are you fucking?

44:13.517 --> 44:15.142
What? What are you talking about?

44:15.352 --> 44:18.062
Come on, I saw you gazing out the
window.

44:18.105 --> 44:19.856
I know it's not Tori.
Who is it?

44:21.191 --> 44:22.358
Nobody?

44:23.485 --> 44:25.069
Well I guess you're free then.

44:27.281 --> 44:29.031
Come on, Zach. You're all I've got.

44:30.242 --> 44:31.325
I know.

44:43.005 --> 44:43.921
Hey.

44:44.089 --> 44:45.798
Hey. Everything cool?

44:47.134 --> 44:48.676
Yeah, yeah...

44:49.553 --> 44:51.679
Uh, what are you doin'?

44:52.306 --> 44:53.639
Going to work.

44:54.600 --> 44:57.810
- Come on over tonight. I'll cook
steaks.

44:58.979 --> 45:01.314
