45:01.481 --> 45:03.608
Come on. I'll make margaritas.

45:03.859 --> 45:05.192
Strong ones.

45:07.195 --> 45:08.279
Who is that?

45:08.530 --> 45:09.614
No one.

45:10.324 --> 45:11.449
Hold on.

45:11.867 --> 45:13.242
So you can do it, right?

45:13.827 --> 45:15.328
I gotta tell Alan.

45:19.708 --> 45:21.375
Fine.
-Cool, thanks.

45:26.590 --> 45:28.090
Shaun, I can't.

45:28.258 --> 45:29.383
Why?

45:29.593 --> 45:32.261
Jeannie's leaving for the weekend
and I gotta watch Cody.

45:32.304 --> 45:33.679
- So bring him.
No.

45:33.972 --> 45:35.097
Why not?

45:37.893 --> 45:39.393
You don't care?

45:39.561 --> 45:41.187
No! That kid's great.

45:41.355 --> 45:42.813
He says some funny shit.

45:43.148 --> 45:45.191
Look, I'm turning the grill on at 8.

45:48.654 --> 45:49.695
Ok.

45:55.869 --> 45:56.953
Come on, dude.

46:03.210 --> 46:05.044
I like these!
I like these!

46:07.089 --> 46:08.923
Nah, you don't want those.

46:13.261 --> 46:14.845
I think you should get these.

46:15.013 --> 46:16.305
But I want real shoes.

46:16.348 --> 46:17.682
But these are way cooler.

46:18.809 --> 46:19.809
Ok.

46:20.227 --> 46:21.727
Alright, let's go.

46:27.275 --> 46:30.194
Hey! Ankle biter!
What's up man, how are ya?

46:30.529 --> 46:33.030
Are you hungry?

46:33.198 --> 46:34.365
