46:34.533 --> 46:36.367
Starvin'? What do you want
for dinner?

46:37.160 --> 46:38.703
Hey, he'll eat whatever.

46:38.870 --> 46:40.579
I don't think I was asking him, was I?

46:40.622 --> 46:42.623
- No.
- No, I don't think so.

46:42.791 --> 46:43.541
No.

46:44.459 --> 46:45.876
Cold ones are in the fridge.

46:46.044 --> 46:47.128
What are you drinking?

46:47.295 --> 46:49.797
Red. Larry had this sick bottle
in the cellar.

46:50.007 --> 46:50.923
I'll try that.

46:51.091 --> 46:52.091
Alright, cool.

46:53.510 --> 46:55.302
Alright, buddy. Lay it on me.

46:55.470 --> 46:56.887
Whatcha gonna have for
dinner tonight?

46:57.055 --> 46:58.597
Uh, Mac and Cheese...

46:58.849 --> 46:59.598
Ok.

47:00.225 --> 47:01.517
Hot dog.

47:01.560 --> 47:02.768
Hot dogs?

47:02.936 --> 47:08.065
And, um, pancakes with...

47:08.233 --> 47:09.775
- Ok!
Chocolate chips.

47:09.818 --> 47:10.901
Chocolate chips? Ok!

47:11.069 --> 47:12.319
and no vegetables.

47:12.487 --> 47:14.572
No vegetables?
Are you sure?

47:15.699 --> 47:16.741
Sure, sure?

47:17.242 --> 47:18.701
Ok. Alright, buddy.

47:18.869 --> 47:20.327
I want you to do me a favor...

47:20.370 --> 47:21.537
Go look out at the ocean.

47:21.788 --> 47:24.832
Beautiful waves coming in right now.
I'm gonna make your dinner.

47:25.042 --> 47:25.833
Somehow.

47:26.376 --> 47:29.879
- Are we still in California?
- Yeah, buddy.

47:31.256 --> 47:32.840
Where are you going?

47:33.592 --> 47:36.135
I don't think we have that stuff
in the house.

47:36.386 --> 47:39.263
Seriously, dude. Don't worry about it.
-No, I want to. I want to.

47:39.431 --> 47:41.182
Little kids are supposed to
be spoiled.

47:41.349 --> 47:43.934
Besides, I'll be back in like five
minutes, ok?

47:44.561 --> 47:46.145
I'm gonna go check on him.

47:50.484 --> 47:53.110
- Where did Jeanne say she was going?
- She's going to Oregon.

47:53.278 --> 47:55.780
She thinks there's some job
up there worth checking out.

47:57.657 --> 47:59.450
I admire what you're doing for Cody.

48:00.202 --> 48:01.535
You don't have to.

48:03.163 --> 48:05.372
Yeah. I do.

48:06.750 --> 48:08.125
It's a choice, Zach.

48:10.170 --> 48:11.295
It's family.

48:12.756 --> 48:14.340
I'm the only one left.

48:17.636 --> 48:19.678
