01:11:17.806 --> 01:11:20.683
Jeannie, get up!
Get up!

01:11:22.769 --> 01:11:24.145
What are you doing?

01:11:24.313 --> 01:11:25.354
Sleeping.

01:11:26.231 --> 01:11:28.149
Yeah, with some help.

01:11:29.568 --> 01:11:31.861
Wait, Zach, wait.

01:11:32.988 --> 01:11:35.156
Allen got that job.

01:11:35.157 --> 01:11:36.199
Yeah?

01:11:36.783 --> 01:11:40.328
In Portland and I gotta go with him.

01:11:42.539 --> 01:11:44.415
I can make good money there,
and...

01:11:46.585 --> 01:11:48.085
But they don't take kids.

01:11:50.214 --> 01:11:52.256
What do you mean they don't take kids?

01:11:52.466 --> 01:11:55.551
I don't know.
They just don't take kids.

01:11:59.973 --> 01:12:02.558
Allen's not really into it anyway.

01:12:07.356 --> 01:12:10.858
Cody's gonna have to stay
here with you and Papi...

01:12:11.693 --> 01:12:13.152
At least until we get set up.

01:12:13.654 --> 01:12:15.404
With me and dad for how long?

01:12:16.281 --> 01:12:19.075
I dunno. Six months... a year maybe?

01:12:21.286 --> 01:12:23.120
You know he can't stay with dad.

01:12:27.960 --> 01:12:29.043
I know.

01:12:32.005 --> 01:12:33.589
But he can't come with me.

01:12:38.178 --> 01:12:41.889
Zach, the Oceanette is not cutting it.
I can make three times that up there.

01:12:55.153 --> 01:12:56.404
Is there any more?

01:12:58.657 --> 01:12:59.991
Well I'm full, do you want mine?

01:12:59.992 --> 01:13:01.033
Yeah.

01:13:01.868 --> 01:13:03.411
I do.

01:13:03.954 --> 01:13:04.996
You like it?

01:13:05.080 --> 01:13:06.080
Yeah.

01:13:08.250 --> 01:13:10.418
- Mom?
- Yeah.

01:13:10.460 --> 01:13:12.461
Can I go to Oregon too?

01:13:16.341 --> 01:13:18.092
Cody, I told you.
You gotta stay here

01:13:18.135 --> 01:13:20.595
and keep your uncle Zach company
so he doesn't get lonely.

01:13:23.181 --> 01:13:24.974
Can you do that for mommy?

01:13:33.066 --> 01:13:34.108
Hello?

01:13:34.776 --> 01:13:36.235
No, he's not here.

01:14:35.629 --> 01:14:36.796
Hey, monkey.

01:14:37.881 --> 01:14:39.340
Hey.

01:14:43.428 --> 01:14:44.553
I got in.

01:14:44.971 --> 01:14:46.013
What?

01:14:46.431 --> 01:14:47.973
To CalArts, they took me back.

01:14:51.687 --> 01:14:53.104
I don't know how I'll do it.

01:14:53.397 --> 01:14:54.855
You'll have to figure out a way.

01:14:55.065 --> 01:14:57.108
If you pass it up
You'll be stuck here.

01:14:57.984 --> 01:14:59.527
I don't feel stuck here.

01:14:59.611 --> 01:15:00.986
Yes you do.

01:15:04.533 --> 01:15:05.908
Jeanne wants to go to Oregon.

01:15:06.326 --> 01:15:08.035
Maybe she'll have to stay.

01:15:08.286 --> 01:15:09.995
Cody is her responsibility.

01:15:11.832 --> 01:15:13.290
I can't leave him.

01:15:14.793 --> 01:15:16.127
Figure it out.

01:15:17.129 --> 01:15:18.337
Cheer up!

01:15:19.506 --> 01:15:21.465
Can we just celebrate?

01:15:27.264 --> 01:15:29.265
There's something I really
need to tell you.

01:15:30.809 --> 01:15:32.184
I already know.

01:15:34.312 --> 01:15:35.855
I've known for a while.

01:15:40.110 --> 01:15:42.737
You are the only reason
I wish I wasn't.

01:15:43.196 --> 01:15:46.365
None of this other shit matters.

01:15:49.327 --> 01:15:50.953
But what really sucks...

01:15:52.038 --> 01:15:55.166
Is that I've always wanted to
be everything to you.

01:15:59.212 --> 01:16:02.673
Always dreamed of providing you with
anything you ever wanted or needed.

01:16:07.387 --> 01:16:08.554
Do you love him?

01:16:08.847 --> 01:16:09.847
Oh come on...

01:16:09.973 --> 01:16:11.056
Seriously.

01:16:11.433 --> 01:16:13.017
He's a good guy, Zach.

01:16:15.771 --> 01:16:17.855
You don't belong to people forever.

01:16:20.650 --> 01:16:22.234
Then why bother?

01:16:22.611 --> 01:16:23.986
Isn't it worth it?

01:16:27.199 --> 01:16:28.240
Yeah.

01:16:31.661 --> 01:16:33.245
- Tori.
- Yeah?

01:16:35.874 --> 01:16:37.750
Can I stay with you
just for the night?

01:16:39.336 --> 01:16:41.587
I have nowhere else to go and
I can't face Jeanne.

01:16:42.672 --> 01:16:43.714
Of course.

01:16:45.801 --> 01:16:47.426
But you can't fuck me.

01:16:48.720 --> 01:16:49.762
Come on...

01:16:58.563 --> 01:17:03.067
♪ I took a long hard look
At the words in that book ♪

01:17:03.235 --> 01:17:08.948
♪ I had to cast my last stone
And take the long way home ♪

01:17:14.579 --> 01:17:20.084
♪ I couldn't look you in the eye
And tell another lie ♪

01:17:20.252 --> 01:17:22.628
♪ Have to do this on my own ♪

01:17:22.796 --> 01:17:25.923
♪ I'll take the long way home ♪

01:17:27.968 --> 01:17:30.636
♪ the long way home ♪

01:17:37.519 --> 01:17:40.020
♪ I don't know how you feel ♪

01:17:40.188 --> 01:17:45.359
♪ Or if I ever will, yeah
Do you wait by the phone ♪

01:17:45.527 --> 01:17:50.114
♪ While I take the long way home,
the long way home ♪

01:17:52.784 --> 01:17:54.326
Say something.

01:17:57.956 --> 01:17:59.206
You say something.

01:17:59.791 --> 01:18:03.127
Student was bad.
Made bad judgment call.

01:18:04.588 --> 01:18:06.046
Now see truth.

01:18:10.969 --> 01:18:12.052
Where are you?

01:18:13.930 --> 01:18:15.306
Getting warmer...

01:18:16.099 --> 01:18:17.099
Colder...

01:18:20.687 --> 01:18:21.896
Turn around.

01:18:27.068 --> 01:18:28.235
I'm so sorry.

01:18:34.159 --> 01:18:35.576
You'd better be.

01:18:40.373 --> 01:18:41.916
You sent in my application?

01:18:44.169 --> 01:18:45.210
Yeah.

01:18:52.636 --> 01:18:53.886
Why are you here?

01:18:54.930 --> 01:18:56.138
What changed?

01:18:58.600 --> 01:19:00.100
I did.

01:19:03.355 --> 01:19:04.563
Will you help me?

01:19:06.149 --> 01:19:08.192
You serious?

01:19:09.277 --> 01:19:11.111
Of course.
Anything.

01:19:12.322 --> 01:19:13.447
Anything?

01:19:13.490 --> 01:19:14.615
Yes.

01:19:18.495 --> 01:19:19.536
I got in.

01:19:19.955 --> 01:19:22.122
- Full ride.
- Yes! I knew it!

01:19:22.540 --> 01:19:24.041
Are you serious?

01:19:24.250 --> 01:19:25.960
Yeah, I really wanna go this time.

01:19:26.044 --> 01:19:27.211
Of course.

01:19:28.046 --> 01:19:30.172
I turned down the scholarship before.

01:19:34.135 --> 01:19:37.721
My mom... Cody... everything.
I just couldn't walk out.

01:19:39.474 --> 01:19:40.766
I never told anyone.

01:19:45.522 --> 01:19:47.022
I really wanna go this time.

01:19:47.732 --> 01:19:50.943
And you did say you lived close.

01:19:53.697 --> 01:19:55.114
Well then let's do it.

01:19:56.157 --> 01:19:58.033
- Yeah?
- Yeah.

01:19:59.703 --> 01:20:04.832
I'm so proud of you, man. So proud.

01:20:37.490 --> 01:20:39.199
- Shaun!
- Hey, kiddo...

01:20:39.242 --> 01:20:41.535
Allen, take Cody inside, ok?

01:20:44.372 --> 01:20:46.540
Zach, what is he doing here?

01:20:50.670 --> 01:20:51.962
What? Are you bailing on me?

01:20:51.963 --> 01:20:53.088
Bailing?

01:20:53.631 --> 01:20:56.258
Jeanne, you're the one
leaving your son!

01:20:57.761 --> 01:20:59.678
If you don't like this option
then just stay.

01:20:59.846 --> 01:21:01.221
Five more minutes!

01:21:01.514 --> 01:21:03.182
Jesus, Cody. Shut the fuck up you...

01:21:03.349 --> 01:21:04.850
Don't you ever talk to him like that!

01:21:04.976 --> 01:21:06.477
- Zach!
- Allen!

01:21:07.896 --> 01:21:09.354
- Zach!
- That fucking little shit!

01:21:09.522 --> 01:21:11.440
Take a walk baby, please?
For me. Please...

01:21:11.775 --> 01:21:13.859
Ok, ok.

01:21:15.653 --> 01:21:18.280
- Easy, easy.
- Zach, what the fuck!

01:21:22.994 --> 01:21:24.161
Jesus Christ.

01:21:27.665 --> 01:21:29.333
I'm gonna go inside and check on him.

01:21:43.723 --> 01:21:45.516
Shaun is really great, Jeanne.

01:21:46.142 --> 01:21:48.310
He really cares about Cody...
and me.

01:21:53.650 --> 01:21:56.068
If he can't be with you,
this is the next best thing.

01:21:59.405 --> 01:22:00.989
I'm gonna make it work.

01:22:08.998 --> 01:22:10.541
Jeanne, take a look around.

01:22:12.377 --> 01:22:15.379
Every kid should be so lucky.

01:22:18.883 --> 01:22:21.426
What else could you possibly
want for him?

01:22:27.934 --> 01:22:29.643
I got into CalArts.

01:22:30.770 --> 01:22:31.854
I know.

01:22:35.650 --> 01:22:36.650
You know?

01:22:37.443 --> 01:22:38.902
Were you gonna tell me?

01:22:41.990 --> 01:22:44.408
They told me that you
turned it down last time.

01:22:45.118 --> 01:22:47.035
I'm not going to again.

01:22:49.330 --> 01:22:50.497
No, you shouldn't.

01:22:54.043 --> 01:22:55.252
He'll be fine with us...

01:22:57.422 --> 01:22:59.506
Or stay, it's your choice.

01:23:02.468 --> 01:23:05.721
Zach, if this thing with Allen
doesn't work out...

01:23:07.223 --> 01:23:09.516
It's best that he's here with you.

01:23:12.437 --> 01:23:14.229
He's in good hands I promise.

01:23:16.983 --> 01:23:18.025
Yeah.

01:23:41.966 --> 01:23:47.596
♪ Take me back toward the sea
Amongst the tide, amongst the sky ♪

01:23:47.764 --> 01:23:51.266
♪ Never thought much of the
