♪ Let's make it like a hideaway ♪

01:24:11.037 --> 01:24:16.875
♪ Take me back to where I'm from
For me there's nothing more ♪

01:24:17.043 --> 01:24:24.925
♪ Take me back to where I'm from
Take me back to where I'm from ♪

